==English==

===Noun===
'''consultant'''
# a person or party that is [[consult]]ed.  
# a person whose occupation is to be consulted for their expertise, advice, or help in an area or 
specialty.  Alternatively, a party whose business is to be similarly consulted.

'''Derived terms: [[consultancy]]'''

